{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_背尸",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·背庄家尸（教学：背尸力学）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "xg_beishi_done",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "literal", "name": "旁白" },
      "text": "不看了。这辈子都不想再看。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "literal", "name": "旁白" },
      "text": "大红嫁衣在烛光底下红得发黑。关二狗啐了口唾沫搓搓手——上前，过肩，搭手。背尸的老把式，闭着眼都不会错。",
      "next": "n_hold"
    },
    "n_hold": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "carry_bride_corpse"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "literal", "name": "旁白" },
      "text": "瘫坐在地上喘气的工夫，鼻尖掠过一缕味儿——浆洗棉布、线头，和一点……廉价香料。",
      "next": "n_cue"
    },
    "n_cue": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "playSignalCue",
          "params": {
            "id": "axiu_faint"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "player" },
      "text": "尸臭俺闻过八百回。这味儿——不是。",
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "literal", "name": "旁白" },
      "text": "凉透骨。重得邪门。停了多日像才刚停下。这尸，哪样都不对劲。头皮一层一层麻上来。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "player" },
      "text": "工钱……工钱个屁！！",
      "next": "n6"
    },
    "n6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "literal", "name": "旁白" },
      "text": "他连滚带爬夺门而出，一口气跑回城，天都蒙蒙亮了。后头四十文的事，再没人提起——他也没敢回去要。",
      "next": "n_flag"
    },
    "n_flag": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "xg_beishi_done",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "雾津街头",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "from_event"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
